    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade example of the R32 Skyline GT-R. The heart of this Godzilla is the legendary RB26DETT inline-six, featuring parallel ceramic turbochargers and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered via the sophisticated ATTESA E-TS all-wheel-drive system and a visceral 5-speed close-ratio manual transmission. This chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its factory-spec multi-link suspension and functional Super HICAS four-wheel steering. Every mechanical component, from the viscous limited-slip differential to the four-piston calipers, operates with factory-new precision. The paint depth and interior upholstery reflect a vehicle preserved in a climate-controlled environment, devoid of typical bolster wear or dash bubbling. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak JDM engineering in its purest form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
