      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve totally babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s been serviced religiously. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, this is the one. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
